race.comment: DARLING CLEMENTINE (2) won a CL1 by a space at Thangool and then was beaten a nose here this grade and a $2.60 favourite. Peaks on a 6-day return and rates to bounce back in this lineup. YES I'M UGLY (7) was tracking well before a plainer effort at Dalby beaten 2.6L. Expect him to settle closer today and he is also on a quick backup. A chance. OUR HEART THROB (12) was beaten 1L in the DARLING CLEMENTINE race making good improvement. Fitter again and will be hitting the line. SANTORINI SUMMER (3) needs a good ride but was better at Mackay last time and he goes into the trifectas on that effort.
